#: ../../source/training/beginner/osm/107-imagery-offset.rst:282
# 9eb1bcd47ea94c26b7ec92a56d147181
msgid "Here we have downloaded OSM data and GPS tracks in Kuta, Bali, Indonesia.  In this case, we have found one existing offset.  Click on it to apply to the map."
